Congrats to our Lake Seminole CHAMPS Corey and Flint catching nearly 25lbs!  Here's what they had to say," We caught a few Texas rigging and Carolina rigging a big Burner Worm, but what was really awesome was the new Slim Easy. I was throwing it in white and could feel them nipping it before they ate it. Once they got behind it, I would tell Corey to get the net, 'cause they about to be on it!"
When asked how they felt about Gambler Lures with a first place check in his pocket, Flint responded, "The check is just an added bonus. I always buy Gambler, 'cause I always catch 'em on Gambler! I look forward to this every year."

With the dominance of forward facing sonar on tour we wanted to design an entire arsenal of tackle specifically designed to give anglers better results when using Livescope or Active Target.  Introducing the FF Series and our first release the Hover Hook and FFS Min-O.  The Hover Hook allows anglers to fish for suspended bass easily with a presentation that practically looks like live bait.  The custom soft plastic blend used in FFS plastics gives a stronger return on forward facing sonar - allowing you to see more and catch more!
